<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/independent-monitoring-authority-for-the-citizens-rights-agreements> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Independent Monitoring Authority for the Citizens’ Rights Agreements (IMA) will work to protect the rights of EU and EEA EFTA (Iceland, Liechtenstein and Norway) citizens in the UK and Gibraltar. IMA is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ."@en .
